\par COUNTY OF ________________
\par 
\par 
\par _____________________, having been sworn or affirmed to tell the truth, states: 
\par 
\par WHEREAS, on ____________, ___________________ executed a power of attorney naming myself as their attorney in fact, and, 
\par 
\par WHEREAS, on _______________ I began to act under that power, and, 
\par 
\par WHEREAS, ________________ is requesting verification that the power is still in force and effect, 
\par 
\par ________________________, having personal knowledge of the facts and circumstances herein, certify that the power of attorney referred to herein is still in full force and effect and that I am not aware of any event which
 would result in the power of attorney lapsing having taken effect. 
